Date: Wed, 8 Jul 2026 00:25:33 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 10/10] =?UTF-8?q?web-app:=20rework=20the=20Rocket=20dev=20?=
 =?UTF-8?q?theme=20=E2=80=94=20centered=20composer,=20RC=20palette,=20slim?=
 =?UTF-8?q?mer=20CSS?=
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Composer: center single-line text/buttons (align-items: center), drop the
order overrides (upstream DOM order already matches Rocket.chat: attach,
text, emoji, mic), stop hiding the send button, RC-blue round send.

Colors: classic Rocket.chat palette — #1d74f5 actions/accent, #2f343d
sidebar + text, #9ea2a8 secondary/metadata (kills the green timestamps),
#f5455c danger; author letter-blocks use the per-contact color instead
of red/black.

CSS diet: prefer theme params over CSS (bgChatView/bgImage replace the
!important background rules, messageOutgoingStatusColor replaces the
metadata recolors), merge the duplicate :root/.composer/.message blocks,
drop dead rules (.navbar-chat-subtile typo, .attachment-overlay,
#action-go-to-login, emojiMartSelect, commented-out block) and fix the
day-marker selector (upstream renders .bubble now, not p).

Co-Authored-By: Claude Fable 5 <noreply@anthropic.com>
